I view this as a matter of pure opinion.  I don't disagree with you,
but I don't think there's a right or wrong way.  I ran SF/F news on
the Escape Pod blog for a while (thanks Mur!) and nobody complained.
Nobody loved it either, and I eventually decided it wasn't worth the
